title: RHOD: Musical Epilogue
description:
We turned the Real Housewives of Dallas into a musical epilogue because we just saw Little Shop of Horrors and can’t stop obsessing. Enjoy! For bonus episodes and extras, become a premium subscriber at http://patreon.com/watchwhatcrappens

See acast.com/privacy for privacy and opt-out information.
